        h1 #{title='Prices and Plans'}
        img.IT(src="/stylesheets/images/cpr-pic.webp")
        p
          | Here at TechAnges we make it our commitment to offer affordable rates. We offer one time services, monthly subscription plans, and yearly subscription plans. 
