          p
            | The cost of the one time services request plan varies by the severity of your issue. An issue that requires a simple and fast fix will likely be at a lower cost than an issue that requires more thorough troubleshooting and support.
          p
          h4 Quick and easy fix 
          p
            | For a quick and simple fix we charge $35. 
            | No upfront payment is required, we offer many back guarantee and free initial analysis. 
          p
