          h3 Advanced Issue 
          p
            | For complex and advanced repairs we charge a one time payment of $50. 
            |This covers computer diagnostic hardware and software repairs. Whether this is sluggish speed, removal of virus and malicious programs, hardcore hardware repairs, and network issues. 
          p
