          h3 Basic subscription plan 
          p
            | This subscription covers all quick and easy fix issues at an affordable rate. No wait is neccessary, call in and you'll have your issue fixed in no time. For basic subscription plan we charge just $10 a month. Computer issues are common, be reassured today knowing you have constant access reliable and supportive assitance. 
          p
